sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Agent as Claude Code / Copilot
    participant Proxy as Transparent Proxy
    participant HookMgr as Hook Manager
    participant Analyzer as Universal Analyzer
    participant Parser as AST Parser (.NET/TSX)
    participant Graph as Dependency Graph Builder
    participant Viz as Local Viz Server (Port 5378)
    participant Cache as SQLite Cache
    participant UI as Status Indicator

    Note over Dev,Agent: Normal Coding Session
    Dev->>Agent: "Add repository pattern to UserService"
    Agent->>Agent: Generate Code
    Agent->>Proxy: Write: UserService.cs / api.tsx
    
    Note over Proxy: Filesystem Intercept
    activate Proxy
    Proxy->>Proxy: Snapshot + Detect Language
    Proxy->>HookMgr: Async ({file, language: csharp|typescript})
    deactivate Proxy
    Agent-->>Dev: "Done!"
    
    Note over HookMgr,Parser: Background Analysis
    HookMgr->>Analyzer: Validate file
    activate Analyzer
    
    alt Language = .NET (C#)
        Analyzer->>Parser: Roslyn AST Parse
        Parser->>Parser: Build Syntax Tree + Symbol Table
        Parser->>Graph: Extract Dependencies
    else Language = React (TSX/JSX)
        Analyzer->>Parser: TypeScript Compiler API / Babel
        Parser->>Parser: Build AST + Component Tree
        Parser->>Graph: Extract Hooks + Props + Context
    end
    
    Graph->>Graph: Build Unified Dependency Graph
    Graph->>Graph: Detect Patterns (Circular, Deep Nesting)
    
    Note over Graph,Viz: Real-time Visualization
    Graph->>Viz: Push to WebSocket Stream
    Viz->>Viz: Update Force-Directed Graph
    Viz-->>Dev: http://localhost:5378
    
    Analyzer->>Analyzer: Compute Rating
    
    alt Rating Drop Detected
        Analyzer->>HookMgr: Violation + Visual Hotspot
        HookMgr->>Agent: Inject Context
        Agent->>Agent: Silent Refactor
        HookMgr->>UI: Update Status
        UI-->>Dev: ● (tooltip: "Arch: 7.3 | Viz: localhost:5378")
    end
    
    Analyzer->>Cache: Store Snapshot + Graph
    deactivate Analyzer